# Emulator data exports and backups
#
# Policy:
# - `emulator-data/` (canonical seeded dev DB) IS tracked in git — shared seed state.
# - Ad-hoc snapshots created on the fly (firebase emulators:export ./.emulator-snapshots/...)
#   live under `.emulator-snapshots/` and are NEVER tracked.
# - Historical exports preserved in `.archive/firebase-exports/` and `.archive/emulator-backups/`
#   ARE tracked (they are bounded historical artifacts, not growing clutter).
#
# Patterns below ignore the LEGACY root-level export folders that Firebase CLI used to drop
# at the repo root. The leading `/` anchors them to root so the `.archive/` copies stay tracked.

/firebase-export-*/
/emulator-data-before-*/
/emulator-data-empty-*/
/emulator-data.backup/
.emulator-snapshots/

# Test/build output files
tsc_output.txt
test_results.txt
tmp/

# TypeScript error logs from previous frontend debug sessions
frontend/ts-errors*.log
frontend/typescript-errors.txt
frontend/build*.log
frontend/build_err*.txt
frontend/build_error.log
